<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<key>StringsTable</key>
	<string>Root</string>
	<key>PreferenceSpecifiers</key>
	<array>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSGroupSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Mode</string>
			<key>FooterText</key>
			<string>Pick how iInteract behaves:

• Default — Bundled panels only, no editing. Best for handing the device to a child.

• Configurable — Hide and reorder the bundled panels.

• Customize — Add your own panels with custom pictures and voice recordings.

Your choice syncs across your iCloud devices.</string>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSMultiValueSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Mode</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>configuration_mode</string>
			<key>Titles</key>
			<array>
				<string>Default — child-safe</string>
				<string>Configurable — hide / reorder</string>
				<string>Customize — your own panels</string>
			</array>
			<key>ShortTitles</key>
			<array>
				<string>Default</string>
				<string>Configurable</string>
				<string>Customize</string>
			</array>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<string>default</string>
			<key>Values</key>
			<array>
				<string>default</string>
				<string>configurable</string>
				<string>custom</string>
			</array>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSGroupSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Voice</string>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSToggleSwitchSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Enable Sound</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>voice_enabled</string>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<true/>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSMultiValueSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Voice Style</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>voice_style</string>
			<key>Titles</key>
			<array>
				<string>Girl</string>
				<string>Boy</string>
			</array>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<string>girl</string>
			<key>Values</key>
			<array>
				<string>girl</string>
				<string>boy</string>
			</array>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSGroupSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Security</string>
			<key>FooterText</key>
			<string>Toggling Enable PIN sends you back to iInteract to set a new PIN (4–8 letters or numbers, with confirmation), or to enter the current PIN to disable it. The PIN is hashed before storage and syncs across your iCloud devices.

Change PIN sends you back to iInteract to verify your current PIN, then enter a new one. The toggle clears itself once you finish or cancel.

Hide Configuration removes the gear icon from the main screen so children can't see configuration exists. Toggle it off here to bring the gear back.</string>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSToggleSwitchSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Enable PIN</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>pin_enabled</string>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<false/>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSToggleSwitchSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Change PIN</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>change_pin</string>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<false/>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSToggleSwitchSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Hide Configuration</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>hide_config</string>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<false/>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSGroupSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Privacy</string>
			<key>FooterText</key>
			<string>When this is on and you return to iInteract, the app asks you to confirm and then permanently removes every custom panel, picture, recording, trashed item, and PIN. Bundled panels are not affected.</string>
		</dict>
		<dict>
			<key>Type</key>
			<string>PSToggleSwitchSpecifier</string>
			<key>Title</key>
			<string>Clear All My Data on Resume</string>
			<key>Key</key>
			<string>pending_clear_all</string>
			<key>DefaultValue</key>
			<false/>
		</dict>
	</array>
</dict>
</plist>
